title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E19 Secret of the Deep
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea

S04E19
Secret of the Deep

Airdate: February 11, 1968

- One of 26 episodes from Season Four which are not yet on DVD
- Remastered audio and video from VHS

Nelson (Richard Basehart) searches for an underwater lab that is threatening the maritime nations of the world.

Crane: David Hedison. Hendrix: Mark Richman. Morton: Bob Dowdell. Patterson: Paul Trinka. Kowalski: Del Monroe. Sharkey: Terry Becker.
